		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello!<br /><br />I wrote an NES port of the Lights Out handheld game. It has 50 puzzles from the original. I have tested this only on the FCEUX emulator, so there may be some bugs...<br /><br />The NTSC ROM image and some screenshots are included as attachments.

		
