		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I finally got around to playing this. This is a brilliant puzzle game. I don't know if you originally thought of the concept or are doing like a port of this from another system like 2048, but this game is amazing. <br /><br />It literally hurts my mind to understand the puzzle logic and I like games that challenge me like this. I've only beaten 2 levels so far. <br /><br />I think if you had included a level editor than that would have been the icing on the cake. <br /><br />Very cool.

		

